title: Week 7 Preview, Sully’s Farewell
itunes:title: Week 7 Preview, Sully’s Farewell
description:
Daniel Jeremiah & Bucky Brooks preview all of the games on the NFL Week 7 schedule (1:33). Then, they pick a winner for the top head-to-head matchups for the latest edition of Bucky’s Battle (18:12). DJ & Bucky give their picks for the biggest college football games of Week 8 (23:14). To wrap the show, the guys give their farewell for producer Sean Sullivan, aka Sully, for his last show at the helms and pick the game between his Volunteers against top ranked Alabama, and give you their favorite Sully moments throughout his years on the show (28:15).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
